1293
01:16:53.582 --> 01:16:54.302
High-risk

1294
01:16:55.222 --> 01:16:59.122
individuals, which fortunately is only about 1% of individuals,

1295
01:16:59.582 --> 01:16:59.862
have

1296
01:17:00.682 --> 01:17:04.602
getting close to an inevitability of progressing to a myeloid

1297
01:17:04.622 --> 01:17:08.442
