1300
01:17:14.222 --> 01:17:16.822
Again, that's only 1% of individuals, which is good.

1301
01:17:16.922 --> 01:17:20.062
90% of individuals are in green in the very low-risk group.

1302
01:17:20.462 --> 01:17:24.122
Only a threefold increased risk of developing a myeloid malignancy, which is a very

1303
01:17:24.162 --> 01:17:27.002
