1310
01:17:53.022 --> 01:17:56.862
And this has been validated now in a number of cohorts, but illustrating that

1311
01:17:56.922 --> 01:18:00.502
even in this cohort that was very different from the UK

1312
01:18:00.542 --> 01:18:04.142
Biobank, in that it was older and less healthy,

1313
01:18:05.122 --> 01:18:08.862
the absolute risk of heme malignancy is most affected by this risk

1314
01:18:08.942 --> 01:18:09.182
group,

1315
01:18:10.202 --> 01:18:14.022
