1319
01:18:27.542 --> 01:18:31.182
So just wanted to note that, again, CHIP is

1320
01:18:31.302 --> 01:18:35.182
extremely common, associated with overall mortality, increased risk of a variety

1321
01:18:35.262 --> 01:18:38.542
